# Expo/Metro (and @expo/cli) resolve some build-tooling deps by walking node_modules,
# which pnpm's default isolated layout hides. Hoist ONLY that tooling to the root
# node_modules. React / React Native are intentionally NOT hoisted: the web apps use
# React 18 and the native app uses React 19, and hoisting would flatten them into one
# copy and break rendering ("multiple copies of React"). Keeping pnpm's isolation lets
# each app resolve its own single React.
public-hoist-pattern[]=*metro*
public-hoist-pattern[]=@babel/runtime
public-hoist-pattern[]=*eslint*
public-hoist-pattern[]=*prettier*
